---
// Mission section component for Mobility Trailblazers
---

<section class="mission" id="about">
	<!-- Subtle wave divider at top -->
	<div class="section-divider-top">
		<svg viewBox="0 0 1200 80" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" preserveAspectRatio="none">
			<path d="M0,40 C300,80 900,0 1200,40 L1200,0 L0,0 Z" fill="#F8F0E3"></path>
		</svg>
	</div>
	<div class="container">
		<div class="mission-grid">
			<div class="mission-content">
				<div class="mission-box">
					<h3 class="mission-prefix">Unsere Mission</h3>
					<h2 class="mission-title" style="color: #004C5F;">Warum «25 Mobility Trailblazers In 25»?</h2>
					<p class="mission-description">
						Wirtschaft, Gesellschaft und Politik im DACH-Raum müssen sich der Mobilitätswende stellen, sollen Wettbewerbsfähigkeit und Wohlstand behauptet werden. Doch Wandel braucht Mut. Unsere Auszeichnung gibt Persönlichkeiten eine Bühne, die vorangehen.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="mission-criteria">
				<h3 class="criteria-title">Was zeichnet Mobility Trailblazers aus?</h3>
				<ul class="criteria-list">
					<li class="criteria-item">
						<i class="fas fa-circle criteria-icon"></i>
						<span>Menschen, die mit <strong>Mut und Wirkung</strong> den Mobilitätswandel gestalten</span>
					</li>
					<li class="criteria-item">
						<i class="fas fa-circle criteria-icon"></i>
						<span><strong>Visionäre</strong> aus Start-ups, etablierten Unternehmen, öffentlicher Verwaltung oder Politik</span>
					</li>
					<li class="criteria-item">
						<i class="fas fa-circle criteria-icon"></i>
						<span>Persönlichkeiten, die <strong>neue Wege</strong> gehen – und Vorbild und Inspiration für andere sind</span>
					</li>
					<li class="criteria-item">
						<i class="fas fa-circle criteria-icon"></i>
						<span>Menschen, die mit ihren Projekten <strong>spürbare Veränderungen</strong> anstoßen</span>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.mission {
		background: var(--color-background);
		position: relative;
		padding: 3rem 0;
	}

	.section-divider-top {
		position: absolute;
		top: -1px;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translateX(-50%);
		width: 100%;
		max-width: none;
		overflow: hidden;
		line-height: 0;
		z-index: 2;
	}

	.section-divider-top svg {
		position: relative;
		display: block;
		width: 100%;
		height: 40px;
	}

	@media (min-width: 768px) {
		.section-divider-top svg {
			height: 60px;
		}
	}

	.mission::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		right: 0;
		bottom: 0;
		background: url('/images/background.webp') center center/cover;
		opacity: 0.1;
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.mission-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 3rem;
		align-items: stretch;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 2;
	}

	.mission-content {
		position: relative;
		display: flex;
		align-items: stretch;
	}

	.mission-box {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7));
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
		border-radius: 20px;
		padding: 2rem;
		box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.mission-prefix {
		color: var(--color-accent);
		font-size: 1rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 2px;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		text-align: left;
	}

	.mission-title {
		color: var(--color-primary);
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		line-height: 1.2;
		text-align: left;
	}

	.mission-description {
		color: var(--color-text);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		margin: 0;
		text-align: left;
	}

	.mission-criteria {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
		border-radius: 20px;
		padding: 2rem;
		box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		height: 100%;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
	}

	.criteria-title {
		color: var(--color-primary);
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		text-align: left;
	}

	.criteria-list {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1rem;
		flex: 1;
	}

	.criteria-item {
		display: flex;
		align-items: flex-start;
		gap: 1rem;
		padding: 0.75rem;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
		border-radius: 10px;
		transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
	}

	.criteria-item:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	}

	.criteria-icon {
		color: var(--color-accent);
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		margin-top: 0.3rem;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.criteria-item span {
		color: var(--color-text);
		font-size: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.criteria-item strong {
		color: var(--color-primary);
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.mission-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 2rem;
		}

		.mission-box,
		.mission-criteria {
			padding: 2rem;
		}

		.mission-title {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.criteria-title {
			font-size: 1.5rem;
		}

		.criteria-item {
			padding: 0.8rem;
		}
	}
</style>
